them and you can't study,

13:31.440 --> 13:33.447
but they're great for social purposes.

13:33.567 --> 13:36.631
And I have to go to work
now, like a normal person,

13:36.631 --> 13:37.789
so you have to go.

13:37.832 --> 13:39.165
You didn't meet any girls there?

