13:44.308 --> 13:46.142
You know, maybe you
should go out some time.

13:46.185 --> 13:48.369
Have you met somebody
that you would go out with?

13:48.388 --> 13:49.502
Maybe you could call them

13:49.514 --> 13:52.905
and that would give you another
reason to get out of my room

13:53.118 --> 13:54.951
other than I have to go to work.

13:55.545 --> 13:56.446
What? Have you?

13:56.484 --> 13:59.300
