14:06.062 --> 14:08.859
Nice you can forget, I can't forget.

14:08.865 --> 14:12.570
And, just for the record, I was
forced into doing what I did!

14:12.595 --> 14:14.484
I know, I know, I said I was sorry.

14:14.515 --> 14:16.561
I'm never going to have
a normal life, you know,

14:16.580 --> 14:18.006
